3C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Savannah Neibart\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"textpartnumber\" id=\"aba\">section a\u003C/span>\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"diva--diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"textpartnumber\">face a\u003C/span>\u003Ca id=\"aa-l1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>ΘΕΑ\u003Cbr id=\"aa-l2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κλεοννο̄́\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"idionym\" data-text=\"Κλεοννο̄́\">Κ.ΕΟΝΝΟ̄\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"aa-l3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>.ΟΤΙΚΑΛ\u003Cbr id=\"aa-l4-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>..Ν.[.]\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cspan class=\"textpartnumber\" id=\"abb\">section b\u003C/span>\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"divb--diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"textpartnumber\">face b\u003C/span>\u003Ca id=\"ab-l1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἀθο̄́νυμος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"idionym\" data-text=\"Ἀθο̄́νυμος\">ΑΘΟ̄ΝΥΜΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"ab-l2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Συλιν Σίμο̄\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"idionym\" data-text=\"Συλιν\">ΣΥΛΙΝ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Σίμο̄\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Σίμο̄\">ΣΙΜΟ̄\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic030087_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic030087_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic030087.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic030087-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>  \u003Cspan>Text after Bettarini.\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>  \u003C/p>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>  \u003C/p>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>Tra gli aspetti più interessanti del recto c'è l'intestazione θεά: che si tratti di un'intestazione è confermato dal fatto che la parola è stata incisa nella prima riga di scrittura in posizione centrale, mentre le righe successive cominciano tutte vicino al margine sinistro della lamina. L'identificazione di questa dea è scontata: si tratta ovviamente di Persefone, associata nel culto a Demetra Malophoros, dal cui santuario in località Gaggera provengono molte defixiones. Non è comune intestare le defixiones (sebbene vi sia l'esemplare geloo che inizia con tyka). La presenza di un'intestazione è solo uno di quegli artifici (come il ricorso a liste incolonnate e ad abbreviazioni) che aveva lo scopo di conferire ufficialità alla pratica privata e segreta della magia nera. (Bettarini)\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 55.1020 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Bettarini 2005 1 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001388\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001388\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\">  Line 1    \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[207,210,213,216,219,221,224,227,230],{"id":208,"html":209},"editions","\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Savannah Neibart\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  \u003Cspan class=\"textpartnumber\" id=\"aba\">section a\u003C/span>  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"diva--interpretive\">  \u003Cspan class=\"textpartnumber\">face a\u003C/span>  \u003Ca id=\"aa-l1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>θεά \u003Cbr id=\"aa-l2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κλεοννο̄́\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"idionym\" data-text=\"Κλεοννο̄́\">Κλ̣εοννο̄́\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"aa-l3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>ͱ̣ότι κα λ-\u003Cbr id=\"aa-l4-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>ο̣̣͂ντ̣[ι] \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cspan class=\"textpartnumber\" id=\"abb\">section b\u003C/span>  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"divb--interpretive\">  \u003Cspan class=\"textpartnumber\">face b\u003C/span>  \u003Ca id=\"ab-l1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἀθο̄́νυμος\">\u003Cspan data-